@DATABASE "Guardian Angel"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - G - Guardian Angel"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - G
                   ====================================

                              Guardian Angel
                              ==============


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPOKE(57626,255)"}          57626,x (x= 1-255)
@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPOKE(59005,0)"}          59005,0
@{"No Enemy      " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPOKE(58756,0)"}          58756,0


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

                         This game was originally known as "Freddy
                         Hardest In South Manhatten" before Code
                         Masters bought it from Dinamic and changed
                         the name (presumably because Ocean brought
                         out the original Freddy). Anyway, the
                         POKEs do work, so that's why you're in
                         a "G" game if you originally started
                         off in the "F" menu OK?


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
